{"title":"Hexo博客部署平台怎么选？","uid":"cd5a154b509f949d9d21f0203ec98252","slug":"Hexo博客部署平台怎么选？","date":"2025-07-17T14:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-07-18T01:38:59.857Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo博客部署平台怎么选？.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/hexo&github.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"为什么部署平台很重要？\"><a href=\"#为什么部署平台很重要？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"为什么部署平台很重要？\"></a>为什么部署平台很重要？</h2><p>Hexo 生成的是一堆静态文件——HTML、CSS、JS、图片。这些文件需要放在某个地方，别人才能通过浏览器访问。这个”放文件的地方”就是部署平台。</p>\n<p>选对平台，你的博客打开速度快、稳定不宕机、搜索引擎收录好；选错平台，读者等半天打不开，你自己维护也头疼。</p>\n<p>市面上能部署 Hexo 的平台很多，但主流的其实就四个：<strong>Vercel</strong>、<strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong>、<strong>Netlify</strong> 和 <strong>GitHub Pages</strong>。下面从实际使用体验出发，逐个分析。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"一、Vercel-——-综合体验最佳\"><a href=\"#一、Vercel-——-综合体验最佳\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、Vercel —— 综合体验最佳\"></a>一、Vercel —— 综合体验最佳</h2><h3 id=\"部署流程\"><a href=\"#部署流程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署流程\"></a>部署流程</h3><p>Vercel 的部署体验可以说是”傻瓜式”的：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>用 GitHub 账号登录 Vercel</li>\n<li>点击”New Project”，导入你的 Hexo 仓库</li>\n<li>Framework Preset 选择 <code>Hexo</code>（Vercel 会自动识别）</li>\n<li>点击 Deploy，等一两分钟就好了</li>\n</ol>\n<p>之后每次你 <code>git push</code> 到主分支，Vercel 会自动触发构建和部署，完全不用手动操作。</p>\n<h3 id=\"优点\"><a href=\"#优点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"优点\"></a>优点</h3><ul>\n<li><strong>速度极快</strong>：Vercel 的全球 CDN 节点分布广泛，Edge Network 覆盖 100+ 城市，国内访问速度在四大平台中排第一</li>\n<li><strong>自动 HTTPS</strong>：默认开启，不用额外配置 SSL 证书</li>\n<li><strong>预览部署</strong>：每次 PR 都会生成一个预览链接，方便你在合并前检查效果</li>\n<li><strong>免费额度 generous</strong>：个人项目基本用不完</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"缺点\"><a href=\"#缺点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"缺点\"></a>缺点</h3><ul>\n<li><strong>默认域名被墙</strong>：<code>*.vercel.app</code> 在国内已经被屏蔽，<strong>必须绑定自己的域名</strong>才能被国内读者访问</li>\n<li><strong>国内节点有限</strong>：虽然有 CDN，但大陆节点不如 Cloudflare 多</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"适合谁\"><a href=\"#适合谁\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"适合谁\"></a>适合谁</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>长期写博客、有自己域名的作者。</strong> 如果你打算认真经营博客，买一个域名（一年几十块），搭配 Vercel 是最省心的方案。</p></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"二、Cloudflare-Pages-——-速度与安全的平衡\"><a href=\"#二、Cloudflare-Pages-——-速度与安全的平衡\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、Cloudflare Pages —— 速度与安全的平衡\"></a>二、Cloudflare Pages —— 速度与安全的平衡</h2><h3 id=\"部署流程-1\"><a href=\"#部署流程-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署流程\"></a>部署流程</h3><p>和 Vercel 几乎一样简单：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>登录 Cloudflare 控制台，进入 Pages</li>\n<li>连接 GitHub 仓库</li>\n<li>构建命令填 <code>hexo generate</code>，输出目录填 <code>public</code></li>\n<li>部署</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Cloudflare 会自动检测 Hexo 项目，大部分情况下连构建命令都不用手动填。</p>\n<h3 id=\"优点-1\"><a href=\"#优点-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"优点\"></a>优点</h3><ul>\n<li><strong>CDN 节点最多</strong>：Cloudflare 在全球有 300+ 数据中心，静态资源分发能力极强</li>\n<li><strong>免费额度极高</strong>：每月 500 次构建、无限带宽，个人博客根本用不完</li>\n<li><strong>自带 DDoS 防护</strong>：Cloudflare 的老本行，安全性没得说</li>\n<li><strong>Workers 生态</strong>：如果你以后想加服务端逻辑（比如评论系统后端），可以直接用 Cloudflare Workers</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"缺点-1\"><a href=\"#缺点-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"缺点\"></a>缺点</h3><ul>\n<li><strong>默认域名被墙</strong>：<code>*.pages.dev</code> 和 <code>*.workers.dev</code> 在国内同样被屏蔽，需要绑定自己的域名</li>\n<li><strong>国内速度略逊 Vercel</strong>：虽然节点多，但实际测试中 Vercel 的 Edge 网络对国内用户更友好一些</li>\n<li><strong>构建速度稍慢</strong>：相比 Vercel 的秒级构建，Cloudflare Pages 有时需要 1-2 分钟</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"适合谁-1\"><a href=\"#适合谁-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"适合谁\"></a>适合谁</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>追求极致稳定性和安全性的作者。</strong> 如果你担心博客被攻击，或者想要最大的免费带宽额度，Cloudflare Pages 是首选。</p></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"三、Netlify-——-零域名门槛的选择\"><a href=\"#三、Netlify-——-零域名门槛的选择\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、Netlify —— 零域名门槛的选择\"></a>三、Netlify —— 零域名门槛的选择</h2><h3 id=\"部署流程-2\"><a href=\"#部署流程-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署流程\"></a>部署流程</h3><p>同样简单：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>登录 Netlify，点击”Add new site” → “Import an existing project”</li>\n<li>连接 GitHub 仓库</li>\n<li>构建命令 <code>hexo generate</code>，输出目录 <code>public</code></li>\n<li>部署</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Netlify 也能自动检测 Hexo，流程和其他平台差不多。</p>\n<h3 id=\"优点-2\"><a href=\"#优点-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"优点\"></a>优点</h3><ul>\n<li><strong>默认域名国内可访问</strong>：<code>*.netlify.app</code> <strong>没有被墙</strong>，这是它最大的优势——你不需要买域名就能让国内读者访问</li>\n<li><strong>表单功能</strong>：Netlify Forms 可以免费处理表单提交，适合做留言板、联系表单</li>\n<li><strong>Split Testing</strong>：支持 A&#x2F;B 测试，适合想做精细化运营的博主</li>\n<li><strong>大文件支持好</strong>：上传大图片、视频等资源时表现不错</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"缺点-2\"><a href=\"#缺点-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"缺点\"></a>缺点</h3><ul>\n<li><strong>速度一般</strong>：CDN 节点数量和覆盖范围不如 Vercel 和 Cloudflare，国内访问速度排第三</li>\n<li><strong>免费额度有限</strong>：每月 100GB 带宽，如果你的博客图片很多、流量很大，可能不够用</li>\n<li><strong>构建队列排队</strong>：免费用户在高峰期构建可能需要排队等待</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"适合谁-2\"><a href=\"#适合谁-2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"适合谁\"></a>适合谁</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>不想买域名、只想快速把博客跑起来的作者。</strong> 如果你暂时不想花钱，Netlify 是唯一一个默认域名在国内能正常访问的平台。</p></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"四、GitHub-Pages-——-最简单但也最慢\"><a href=\"#四、GitHub-Pages-——-最简单但也最慢\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、GitHub Pages —— 最简单但也最慢\"></a>四、GitHub Pages —— 最简单但也最慢</h2><h3 id=\"部署流程-3\"><a href=\"#部署流程-3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"部署流程\"></a>部署流程</h3><p>GitHub Pages 的”简单”体现在零成本、零门槛：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>创建一个名为 <code>用户名.github.io</code> 的仓库</li>\n<li>把 Hexo 生成的 <code>public</code> 目录内容 push 上去</li>\n<li>在仓库 Settings → Pages 中开启 GitHub Pages</li>\n</ol>\n<p>但要注意，GitHub Pages <strong>不支持自动构建 Hexo 项目</strong>（它只原生支持 Jekyll 和纯静态文件）。你需要用 GitHub Actions 来实现自动构建：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">name: Deploy Hexo\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\njobs:\n  deploy:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions&#x2F;checkout@v4\n      - uses: actions&#x2F;setup-node@v4\n        with:\n          node-version: 20\n      - run: npm install &amp;&amp; npx hexo generate\n      - uses: peaceiris&#x2F;actions-gh-pages@v4\n        with:\n          github_token: $&#123;&#123; secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN &#125;&#125;\n          publish_dir: .&#x2F;public</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"优点-3\"><a href=\"#优点-3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"优点\"></a>优点</h3><ul>\n<li><strong>完全免费</strong>：没有带宽限制（合理范围内），没有构建次数限制</li>\n<li><strong>域名友好</strong>：<code>*.github.io</code> 国内可以访问，不需要额外买域名</li>\n<li><strong>生态成熟</strong>：用的人最多，遇到问题搜一搜基本都能找到解决方案</li>\n<li><strong>与 GitHub 深度集成</strong>：代码和部署在同一个平台，管理方便</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"缺点-3\"><a href=\"#缺点-3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"缺点\"></a>缺点</h3><ul>\n<li><strong>速度慢</strong>：只有一个美国服务器，没有真正的全球 CDN，国内访问速度最慢</li>\n<li><strong>配置麻烦</strong>：需要自己写 GitHub Actions，对新手不友好</li>\n<li><strong>自定义域名需要额外配置 DNS</strong>：虽然支持自定义域名，但配置过程比 Vercel&#x2F;Cloudflare 复杂</li>\n<li><strong>HTTPS 配置繁琐</strong>：自定义域名时需要手动处理 SSL 证书</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"适合谁-3\"><a href=\"#适合谁-3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"适合谁\"></a>适合谁</h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>预算为零、不介意速度慢的作者。</strong> 如果你只是写着玩，不在乎读者打开速度，GitHub Pages 够用。</p></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"五、其他部署方式\"><a href=\"#五、其他部署方式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、其他部署方式\"></a>五、其他部署方式</h2><p>除了上面四个主流平台，还有一些值得了解的部署方案：</p>\n<h3 id=\"VPS-自建服务器\"><a href=\"#VPS-自建服务器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"VPS 自建服务器\"></a>VPS 自建服务器</h3><p>如果你有一台云服务器（阿里云、腾讯云、AWS 等），可以直接用 Nginx 托管静态文件。Hexo 生成 <code>public</code> 目录后，通过 <code>rsync</code> 或 <code>scp</code> 上传到服务器。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"># 安装 hexo-deployer-rsync 后，在 _config.yml 中配置\ndeploy:\n  type: rsync\n  host: 你的服务器IP\n  user: root\n  root: &#x2F;usr&#x2F;share&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;html\n  port: 22\n  delete: true\n  verbose: true</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>优点</strong>：完全自主可控，速度取决于服务器位置，可以放国内节点</li>\n<li><strong>缺点</strong>：需要自己维护服务器、配置 Nginx、处理 SSL 证书、防范攻击，成本较高（服务器费用）</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"对象存储-CDN（阿里云-OSS-x2F-腾讯云-COS）\"><a href=\"#对象存储-CDN（阿里云-OSS-x2F-腾讯云-COS）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"对象存储 + CDN（阿里云 OSS &#x2F; 腾讯云 COS）\"></a>对象存储 + CDN（阿里云 OSS &#x2F; 腾讯云 COS）</h3><p>把 <code>public</code> 目录上传到对象存储（如阿里云 OSS、腾讯云 COS），再绑定 CDN 加速。适合流量大、对成本控制有要求的场景。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>优点</strong>：按量付费，流量大时比 VPS 便宜；CDN 节点多，国内覆盖好</li>\n<li><strong>缺点</strong>：配置复杂度高，需要分别配置存储桶、CDN、域名、SSL，有一定学习成本</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"Surge-sh-——-极简-CLI-部署\"><a href=\"#Surge-sh-——-极简-CLI-部署\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Surge.sh —— 极简 CLI 部署\"></a>Surge.sh —— 极简 CLI 部署</h3><p>Surge 是一个命令行部署工具，一行命令就能把静态站点发布到互联网：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install -g surge\ncd public\nsurge</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>优点</strong>：部署速度极快，适合临时预览或快速分享</li>\n<li><strong>缺点</strong>：功能单一，没有自动构建，免费域名 <code>*.surge.sh</code> 国内访问不稳定</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"综合对比\"><a href=\"#综合对比\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"综合对比\"></a>综合对比</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>维度</th>\n<th>Vercel</th>\n<th>Cloudflare Pages</th>\n<th>Netlify</th>\n<th>GitHub Pages</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>部署难度</strong></td>\n<td>极简</td>\n<td>极简</td>\n<td>极简</td>\n<td>需配置 Actions</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>国内访问速度</strong></td>\n<td>最快</td>\n<td>很快</td>\n<td>一般</td>\n<td>最慢</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>默认域名国内可用</strong></td>\n<td>被墙</td>\n<td>被墙</td>\n<td>可用</td>\n<td>可用</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>免费带宽</strong></td>\n<td>100GB&#x2F;月</td>\n<td>无限</td>\n<td>100GB&#x2F;月</td>\n<td>无限（合理范围）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>自动 HTTPS</strong></td>\n<td>是</td>\n<td>是</td>\n<td>是</td>\n<td>是（自定义域名需手动）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>构建速度</strong></td>\n<td>秒级</td>\n<td>1-2 分钟</td>\n<td>1-3 分钟</td>\n<td>取决于 Actions</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>额外功能</strong></td>\n<td>预览部署、Edge Functions</td>\n<td>DDoS 防护、Workers</td>\n<td>表单、A&#x2F;B 测试</td>\n<td>无</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"我的推荐\"><a href=\"#我的推荐\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"我的推荐\"></a>我的推荐</h2><p><strong>如果你有域名（或愿意买一个）：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>首选 Vercel</strong>，速度最快、体验最好。绑定域名后国内访问完全没问题。Vercel 的 Edge Network 对中文内容的分发优化做得很到位，实际体验比 Cloudflare Pages 更流畅。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>如果你没有域名、不想花钱：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>选 Netlify</strong>。<code>*.netlify.app</code> 在国内能正常访问，部署简单，免费额度对个人博客足够。等以后博客做大了、想更专业了，再买域名迁移到 Vercel 也不迟。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>如果你追求极致安全和稳定性：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>选 Cloudflare Pages</strong>。300+ 数据中心、无限带宽、自带 DDoS 防护，适合对稳定性要求极高的场景。</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>GitHub Pages 的定位：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>作为<strong>备选方案</strong>。它的优势是生态成熟、完全免费，但速度和配置复杂度是硬伤。除非你对 GitHub 生态有强依赖，否则不太推荐作为主力部署平台。</p></blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"迁移建议\"><a href=\"#迁移建议\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"迁移建议\"></a>迁移建议</h2><p>四个平台之间迁移其实很简单——Hexo 生成的 <code>public</code> 目录内容是一样的，换个平台只需要：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>在新平台导入仓库</li>\n<li>配置构建命令（<code>hexo generate</code>）和输出目录（<code>public</code>）</li>\n<li>绑定域名（如果需要）</li>\n<li>修改 DNS 解析</li>\n</ol>\n<p>整个过程半小时就能搞定，不用纠结”选错了怎么办”。</p>\n<hr>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><strong>总结一句话：</strong> 有域名上 Vercel，没域名上 Netlify，要安全上 Cloudflare，零预算上 GitHub Pages，有服务器就上 VPS。</p></blockquote>\n","text":"从速度、稳定性、国内可访问性、配置复杂度四个维度，深度对比 Vercel、Cloudflare Pages、Netlify 和 GitHub Pages 四大 Hexo 部署平台，帮你选出最适合的方案。...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.6k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"},{"name":"部署","slug":"部署","count":1,"path":"api/tags/部署.json"},{"name":"Vercel","slug":"Vercel","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Vercel.json"},{"name":"Cloudflare","slug":"Cloudflare","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Cloudflare.json"},{"name":"Netlify","slug":"Netlify","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Netlify.json"},{"name":"GitHub Pages","slug":"GitHub-Pages","count":1,"path":"api/tags/GitHub-Pages.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%BE%88%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%EF%BC%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">为什么部署平台很重要？</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81Vercel-%E2%80%94%E2%80%94-%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、Vercel —— 综合体验最佳</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">部署流程</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BC%98%E7%82%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">优点</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BC%BA%E7%82%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">缺点</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E8%B0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">适合谁</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item to